Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.03,0:00:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.44,0:00:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好事沒有\N偏偏在黑龍的迷宮裡迷路…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.81,0:00:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會遇上這種事呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.49,0:00:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿…一頭栽進陷阱了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.36,0:00:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿…快解決他們吧，黑龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.81,0:01:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…我到底該怎麼打才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.84,0:01:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶箱?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.37,0:01:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說迷宮裡藏有許多魔法物品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.98,0:01:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用那個就能對付黑龍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.12,0:01:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試試看吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.35,0:01:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍寶寶，去引開一下牠的注意\N上吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.05,0:01:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻…咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.90,0:01:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是傳說中的魔法物品?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.50,0:01:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.14,0:01:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要打倒你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.87,0:01:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看傳說中的魔法物品\N阿富羅的假髮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.41,0:01:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什麼，看招!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.98,0:01:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.23,0:01:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這個大洞是幹嘛的啊
